<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ق ض ب<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٤٠٤٣ - ق ض ب]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>قضَبَ يَقضِب، قَضْبًا، فهو قاضِب، والمفعول مَقْضوب وقَضِيب<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• قضَب الفلاّحُ أغصانَ الكَرْم:</span> قطعها <span class="c1">"قضَب شجرًا"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• قضَب الرَّجُلَ:</span> ضربه بالقَضيب.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>